# Root Cause Analysis

The failed authentication events were generated by intentional incorrect password submissions during testing of the user account `jsmith`.

No evidence was identified indicating:

* Account compromise
* Privilege escalation
* Lateral movement
* Persistence mechanisms
* Malicious activity

The activity was determined to be normal user authentication behavior resulting from invalid credential entry.

